==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Rockling
<hw>Rock"ling</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>Any species of small marine fishes of the genera <gen>Onos</gen>
and <gen>Rhinonemus</gen> (formerly <gen>Motella</gen>), allied to the
cod. They have three or four barbels.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

